OL,3,CDonald Campbell's Bluebird has
OL,4,Creturned to Coniston decades after
OL,5,Cfatal crash
OL,7,FThe world-famous Bluebird K7 has
OL,8,Freturned to Coniston in the Lake
OL,9,FDistrict - decades after the fatal
OL,10,Fcrash which killed pilot Donald
OL,11,FCampbell.
OL,13,FAfter a lengthy and bitter legal
OL,14,Fbattle, the hydroplane has left a
OL,15,FNorth Shields workshop and will go on
OL,16,Fdisplay at Coniston's Ruskin Museum.
OL,18,FWhat happened to Bluebird?
