OL,3,CDonald Campbell's Bluebird has
OL,4,Creturned to Coniston decades after
OL,5,Cfatal crash
OL,7,FOn 4 January 1967, British speed
OL,8,Frecord breaker Donald Campbell was
OL,9,Fpreparing to smash his mark of 267mph
OL,10,Fon water.
OL,12,FHe was aiming to push his record to
OL,13,Fover 300mph, which proved fatal.
OL,15,FMr Campbell was killed when Bluebird
OL,16,Fsomersalted on Coniston Water during
OL,17,Fthe attempt.
