OL,3,CDonald Campbell's Bluebird has
OL,4,Creturned to Coniston decades after
OL,5,Cfatal crash
OL,7,FThe craft was reduced to a wreckage at
OL,8,Fthe bottom of the lake, and North
OL,9,FTyneside engineer Bill Smith became
OL,10,Ffascinated with finding it, and
OL,11,Frestoring it.
OL,13,FMr Smith's dive team recovered the
OL,14,Fwreckage on 8 March 2001, with Mr
OL,15,FCampbell's body recovered on 28 May.
OL,17,FThey had been diving for four years
OL,18,Fbefore they finally found the
OL,19,Fwreckage, and insisted on restoring it
OL,20,Fas close to the original plan as
OL,21,Fpossible.
