OL,7,FWork on the craft ensued by Mr Smith
OL,8,Fand volunteers from Newcastle, and in
OL,9,F2018, Bluebird ran again on the Isle
OL,10,Fof Bute.
OL,12,FOn Saturday 9 March 2024, Bluebird
OL,13,Fmoved from Bill Smith's workshop in
OL,14,FNorth Shields to the Ruskin Museum.
OL,16,FIt was transported on a flatbed lorry
OL,17,Fto Cumbria, after years of
OL,18,Fnegotiations.
