OL,7,FMr Smith said there is "not a chance"
OL,8,Fthat Bluebird would be back on the
OL,9,Fwater in the near future after the
OL,10,Fmove, and expressed disappointment
OL,11,Fthat it will remain in the museum all
OL,12,Fyear round, rather than being used on
OL,13,Fthe water in certain months.
OL,15,FBluebird restorer and engineer Bill
OL,16,FSmith spoke to ITV Tyne Tees and
OL,17,FBorder about the removal of the craft
OL,18,Ffrom his workshop.
