OL,7,FVillagers lined the streets of
OL,8,FConiston as they watched the boat
OL,9,Freturn - including Mr Campbell's
OL,10,Fdaughter, Gina.
OL,12,FMs Campbell returned to Coniston Water
OL,13,Fin 2021 to lay flowers at the lake, on
OL,14,Fwhat would have been her father's
OL,15,F100th birthday.
