OL,7,FAt the time she told ITV Border: "I
OL,8,Fjust think my father left his mark on
OL,9,Feverybody here in this village. You
OL,10,Ftalk about Donald Campbell, and
OL,11,FBluebird and Coniston - the three are
OL,12,Fintrinsically linked.
OL,14,F"My father lays in the graveyard here,
OL,15,Fhis greatest achievements are here on
OL,16,Fthis fabulous piece of water, and here
OL,17,Fwe are, 100 years on since the day he
OL,18,Fwas born, celebrating his birth.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
