OL,7,F"I think we should not look back on at
OL,8,Fhis death, but on his achievements and
OL,9,Flook at the mark he left for all of us
OL,10,Fto enjoy."
OL,12,FA team from Ruskin Museum accompanied
OL,13,Fthe craft on its journey.
