OL,7,FThe vice chairman of the museum, Jeff
OL,8,FCarroll, said: "It will be an
OL,9,Femotional moment for all concerned. We
OL,10,Fare hoping that the removal from Mr
OL,11,FSmith's workshop which has been
OL,12,FBluebird's home for the last 23 years,
OL,13,Fwill be accomplished easily and
OL,14,Fquickly, but the boat must be checked.
OL,16,F"We have to ensure that this priceless
OL,17,Fpiece of Britain's Heritage is
OL,18,Fproperly stowed for its journey to
OL,19,FConiston.
