OL,7,F"We thank Bill and The Bluebird
OL,8,FProject volunteers for the restoration
OL,9,Fwork that they have done and for
OL,10,Fpassing it to the Ruskin Museum, where
OL,11,Fit will be displayed for all to see
OL,12,Fand where it will start the next stage
OL,13,Fof its journey."
